# 系统文件
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# 个人配置
*/.claude/settings.local.json

# 子项目文档目录（不影响根目录 docs/ 知识库）
**/docs/
!/docs/

# shared目录：保留框架，忽略具体内容
shared/status.json
shared/token-*.md
shared/SIMPLIFICATION-SUMMARY.md
shared/docs/*
shared/designs/*
shared/tasks/*.md
shared/reviews/*.md

# ── Harness 运行时状态 ──
.dev-agents/shared/logs/events-*.jsonl
.dev-agents/shared/memory/activeContext.md
.dev-agents/shared/memory/projectContext.md
.dev-agents/shared/memory/systemPatterns.md
.dev-agents/shared/.workflow-state